ite; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他地方，该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/r-e-m-interpol-death-cab-for-cutie-featured-on-la-wildfire-recovery-album-good-music-to-lift-up-los-angeles-3834796">最近为一张新的汇编专辑做出了贡献，</a>旨在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/interpol">Interpol</a>一起受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶野火的</a>影响， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-cab-for-cutie">Death Cab for Cutie</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-postal-service">邮政服务</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/modest-mouse">Modest Mouse</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a> ，Blondshell， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">The Drugs on Drugs War</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mj-lenderman">MJ Lenderman</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-gizzard-and-the-lizard-wizard">King Gizzard，Gizzard和Lizard Wizard Wizard</a> ，Mac Demarco， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mac-demarco">Mac Demarco</a>等。</p><p>同时，香农（Shannon）和纳尔杜奇（Narducy） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-shannon-jason-narducy-and-friends-to-play-r-e-m-s-fables-of-the-reconstruction-on-2025-uk-tour-3833337">将于今年晚些时候因REM的“重建寓言”袭击英国</a>。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmichael-shannon-jason-narducy-tickets%2Fartist%2F5529326" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买门票。</p><p>邮局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-r-e-m-reunite-again-to-perform-pretty-persuasion-at-hometown-concert-3842370">再次团聚，在家乡音乐会上表演“漂亮的说服力”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
