 him ninth place ($26million/£20million, $35million/£27million gross), with <em>Happy Gilmore 2</em> in production for the streamer and rare dramatic performance <em>Spaceman</em> also coming under that agreement. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">Will Smith</a> finds himself in tenth, thanks to the success of <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/bad-boys-ride-or-die"><em>Bad Boys: Ride Or Die</em></a> . </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bad Boys: Ride Or Die - Final Trailer  - Only In Cinemas Now" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uWLNl_KQCAU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Interestingly, younger stars in Hollywood didn&#39;t feature at all in the list. Everyone in the top 20 is over 40 years old, with the average age being 54. 2023&#39;s list saw Sandler in first, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">Margot Robbie&#39;s</a> success with <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>Barbie</em></a> putting her in second.</p><p> This and Kidman&#39;s placing this year are in contrast with 2022, where <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/highest-paid-actors-list-features-no-women-in-the-top-10-3274123">the top ten was dominated by male actors</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dwayne-johnson-and-ryan-reynolds-among-the-highest-paid-actors-of-2024-3842359">Dwayne Johnson and Ryan Reynolds among the highest paid actors of 2024</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
